  "title": "星見編2章2話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_outside-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage2",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_07-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "――以上、私達……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――That’s it for us. We are…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 1.0666666666666669,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "サニーピース、でしたー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sunny Peace!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.470090691248576,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_clap-03.m4a",
          "delay": 2166.6666666666665,
          "startTime": 5.636757357915243
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage2",
      "startTime": 8.103424024581908
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_07-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "それでは引き続き、スーパータケミヤさんでの\nお買いものを楽しんでくださいね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We hope you enjoy your shopping\nat Takemiya Supermarket!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.2034240246,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_07-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "お、お子様には風船もプレゼントしてますーっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-we’re also giving out balloons for the children!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage2",
      "startTime": 13.80342402458191
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_07-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "こちらは本日のセールのチラシになりまーす",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And here’s the flyer for today’s sale!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.870090691248578,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1066.6666666666629,
          "startTime": 19.93675735791524
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage2",
      "startTime": 22.83675735791524
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_07-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（星見市のスーパーから客引きをお願いされた）\n（サニーピースはパフォーマンスを披露していた）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Sunny Peace was asked by a local Hoshimi supermarket）\n（to put on a performance to draw in customers.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.236757357915245,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage2",
      "startTime": 29.103424024581912
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_07-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "…………どうぞー、チラシです～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Here’s a flyer for you…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.103424024581912,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_07-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（怜だけ、笑顔を作ってはいるけど）\n（どこか気持ちが入っていないか……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（While Rei goes through the motions of smiling‚）\n（she alone doesn’t seem very enthusiastic to be here.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.1034240246,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage1",
      "startTime": 38.5827969392
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage2",
      "startTime": 38.5827969392
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_hoshidorm-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 39.07009069124857
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_07-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "スーパーの客引き、ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Draw in customers for a supermarket?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.736757357915245,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_07-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ああ。入り口の前にスペースを作るから\nそこでパフォーマンスしてほしいってお願いだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. They said they’d prepare a space in front of the store entrance‚\nand they want Sunny Peace to perform there.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.8034240246,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_07-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "で、でも……私達なんかが客引きして\nお客さん、来てくれるんでしょうか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "B-but… will our performance be enough\nto draw in customers?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.37009069124857,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_07-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "店先で踊るだけでも目立つし、効果もあると思う\nそれに、みんなの顔を売るチャンスでもある",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m sure you’ll catch people’s attention and have a positive effect.\nPlus‚ it’s a good opportunity to promote all of you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.670090691248575,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_07-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "地元の人達を、味方につける、戦略\n……あり",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A strategy to get the locals on our side…\nI like it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.7034240246,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_07-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "……けど、こういう仕事で顔を売るより\nもっと練習した方がいいんじゃないですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But wouldn‘t we’d be better off practicing\ninstead of trying to promote ourselves with this sort of work?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.1034240246,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_07-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "それに知名度なんて\nグランプリに勝ち上がれば自然と上がりますし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Besides‚ winning the Grand Prix\nwill naturally lead to more exposure.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.83675735791523,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_07-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "怜の言うことももっともだが、アイドルとして\n生き残るには、こういう営業も大事なんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rei has a point‚ but to survive as idols‚\nthese types of jobs are essential.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.0034240246,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_07-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "いくらファンが多くなっても、パフォーマンスの\n\nレベルが低かったら、ライブバトルに勝てませんよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No matter how many fans we may have‚ if our performance level\nisn’t up to par‚ we won’t win any live battles.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.4700906912486,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_07-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "ライブバトルではファンの数も無視できない\nこうしてファンを直接増やせるチャンスは貴重なんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We can’t ignore the role that fans play in live battles‚\nand this is an invaluable opportunity to directly increase those numbers.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.7034240245,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_07-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "…………だからって……\nよりにもよって……なんでこの店……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But why…\nthis store‚ out of all places…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.89881924850258,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_07-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "こういう小さなお仕事も、きっと楽しいよ！\nそれに、なんだか私達らしいし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I bet these little jobs are a lot of fun!\nBesides‚ it kinda suits us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.46548591516921,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_07-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "……私達、らしい？\nどこがですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "….Suits us?\nHow?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.89881924850253,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_07-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "できることから頑張ってみよう、だよ\nまずはやってみよう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Remember we decided to start with what we can do?\nWell‚ let’s start here!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.1654859152,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage2",
      "startTime": 126.13215258183581
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage2",
      "startTime": 126.13215258183581
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage2",
      "startTime": 130.76548591516928
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_07-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（まだ怜は納得はしていなかったみたいだな）\n（まるで存在を隠したがっているようだし）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（It seems Rei is still not convinced.）\n（She seems to be trying to hide her presence as she passes out the flyers.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.7654859152,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_comical-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 132.6654859151692
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "スーパーの店員",
      "speakerNameEn": "Supermarket",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_07-employee001.m4a",
      "text": "……あれ？　怜ちゃんじゃないの、どうしたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rei-chan‚ is that you? What’re you doing here?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.8635887544604,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage2",
      "startTime": 138.41358894519558
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_07-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "――えっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Huh?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.41358894519558,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage2",
      "startTime": 139.98025561186216
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "スーパーの店員",
      "speakerNameEn": "Supermarket",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_07-employee002.m4a",
      "text": "あ、今日客引きしてくれるってアイドルさん\n\n怜ちゃんのいるグループだったのね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ so the idol group coming to perform today\nwas the one that you’re in!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.3802556119,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
